---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import whatsIncludedImage from '@assets/whats-included.svg';
import whatToBringImage from '@assets/what-to-bring.svg';
import whatToExpectImage from '@assets/what-to-expect.svg';
import luckyImage from '@assets/lucky-surf-coach.jpg';
---

<section>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="infos">
      <ul>
        <li>
          <h3 class="small-heading">What's Included</h3>
          <Image src={whatsIncludedImage} alt="" />
          <p>
            <strong>Board</strong> and <strong>rashguard</strong> are included in
            every lesson
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="small-heading">What to bring</h3>
          <Image src={whatToBringImage} alt="" />
          <p>
            Just take <strong>sunscreen</strong>, <strong>water</strong> and good
            energy
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          <h3 class="small-heading">What to expect</h3>
          <Image src={whatToExpectImage} alt="" />
          <p>
            <strong>90 minutes</strong> of guided surfing, safety, and fun guaranteed
          </p>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <article>
      <h3>How I teach</h3>
      <p>
        I’m a certified ISA Level 1 instructor, with experience surfing both in
        Sri Lanka and abroad. My approach is simple: safe, friendly surf
        sessions that help you progress with confidence.
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>Safety first</strong> — calm, supportive coaching so you feel comfortable
          and confident in the water
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Clear guidance</strong> — simple explanations in English, both on
          the beach and in the waves
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Theory to practice</strong> — we break things down on land, then
          apply it in the water
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Local knowledge</strong> — I grew up surfing Hiriketiya and know
          the bay inside out
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Friendly progression</strong> — no pressure, just steady improvement
          while enjoying the ocean
        </li>
      </ul>
      <Image
        src={luckyImage}
        alt="Lucky, certified surf instructor in Hiriketiya, holding a surfboard and smiling"
        width={300}
      />
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    background-color: var(--color-teal-light);
  }

  .content {
  }

  .infos {
    padding-top: 12rem;
    padding-bottom: 12rem;
  }
  .infos ul {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
  }

  .infos ul li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;

    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .infos ul li img {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 22rem;
  }

  @media (min-width: 550px) {
    .infos ul {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }
  }
</style>
